longBusinessSummary: Axita Cotton Limited engages in manufacturing, processing, finishing, and trading of cotton bales, yarns, and seeds in India. It also engages in ginning and pressing of seed cotton on job work basis. The company serves traders, manufacturers, and merchant exporters. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Ahmedabad, India.
